data.description: Are you looking for a home within city limits, but you need garage/storage space? Then look no further. This ranch home offers a 4 bed, 2 bath, 2 car attached garage, 2 car detached garage, and a spacious backyard. Not enjoying high-interest rates? This home has an assumable mortgage at a 3.0% interest rate. The fully finished basement offers large open space for anything you may need. A dry bar and the included pool table make for a great entertaining space. The detached garage is both heated and cooled to make for a great workshop.  A new egress window and front steps were recently installed this summer. Check out the updates sheet for all the details. Call to book your private showing or if you have questions about the assumable loan.
